			<td>5.3.0</td>
			<td>The MySQL Native Driver was added, with support for all MySQL extensions (i.e., mysql, mysqli and PDO_MYSQL). Passing in&nbsp;mysqlnd&nbsp;to the appropriate configure switch enables this support.</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>5.4.0</td>
